00:27:38,840 --> 00:27:40,320
 behavior.

405
00:27:40,320 --> 00:27:42,200
 You gave me so much more, more than I needed.

406
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:43,680
 Now it's time for me to give it back.

407
00:27:43,680 --> 00:27:44,680
 Hope you feel it."

