00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:57,720
 You were not perfect, but the perfect one for me.

411
00:27:57,720 --> 00:28:03,760
 Thank you always believing, always seeing the good side of me.

412
00:28:03,760 --> 00:28:04,760
 Thank you.

